      "text": "Tad fazzija Raële: Es es-\nntu zaur Deewa Zihnischanahm\nr mannu Mahsu zihntinufees/ un\neri ustvarrejuti / un nosanze\ninna Wahrdn Nawtalis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Lea redseja / ka ta\nj mittejupees dsemideht / tad\nhme ta arridsan farvu Kalponi\nilpu / un deve to Jehkabam\nr Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Silpa / Leas Kalpone/\nindeja Jehkabam Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea: tur nahk\nens Pulks / un nosanze winna\nahrdu Gads.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Silpa / Leas Kalpone\nindeja Jehkabam to ohtru\nhlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea:Lab man/\nhsMeitas turrehs man laimi-\nun ta nosanze winna Wahr-\nAhfers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ruhbens gahje Kwee-\nPtauama Laikā/un atradde\naim Laukā / un atneffe tohs\nfawai Mahtei / un Raële\nia uhs Leii / dohd man jelle\nwa Dehta Dudaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna fazzija us to:\na weena masa Leeta / ka tu\nut Wihru effi atnehmusfi/\ngribbi arridsan manna Deh-\nudaim xenit ? tad fazzija\n/ tapehz buhs tam scho\npee tew gullek+ par taiwa\nDudaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Jehkabs Wakkaraā\nuka nahze / tad isgahje Lea\nretti / un fazzija: pee man\new nahkt / jo es ejimu tew\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ar Maffu faderrejust par man-\nna Dehta Dudaim / un wiꞥſch\ngulleja pee tahs tanni Nakti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews paflaufija to\nLeii / un ta tappe gruhta / un\ndsemideja Jehkabam to peektu\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea : Deews\nirr man to maffajs / ka es man-\nnam Wihrum mannu Kalponi\nefunu dewuji/ un ta nosanze win-\nna Wahrdn Jhsafchars.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lea tappe atkaž gruh-\nta/ un dsemideja Jehkabam to fes-\ntu Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea : Deews\nirr man apdahwanajs ar labbu\nDahwanu / scho Brihdi peedsih-\nwohs man mans Wihrs/ tapehz/\nka es winnam setch Dehlus ef-\nnu dsemidejti/ un nosanze winna\nWahrdn Sebulons.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz to dsemideja win-\nna weenu Meitu/un nosanze win-\nnas Wahrdn Dina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews atgahdajahs us\nRaëli / un Deews paflaufija\nwinnu/ un dartja winnu aug-\nligu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna tappe gruhta/\nun dsemideja weenn Dehlu / un\nfazzija : DEews irr mannu Ap-\nsineelu no mannim atnehmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta nosanze winna\nWahrdn Jahseps / fazzidama:\nLard tas KUNGS man apdah-\nwana wehl ar zittu Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notikke / kad Raële\nJahsepu bij dsemidejusi / fazzija\nJehkabs us Lahbanu : atlaid\nman/\n"
    }
